WEBVTT

00:15:00.942 --> 00:15:05.443
JL: Mainly, you know it because you've had
the experience of it not going well.

00:15:05.467 --> 00:15:08.200
The audience tells you an enormous amount.

00:15:08.523 --> 00:15:10.394
Just the sound of an audience.

00:15:10.418 --> 00:15:15.192
People cough and shift
in their seats if they're bored.

00:15:15.216 --> 00:15:17.550
You become a connoisseur of silence.

00:15:18.351 --> 00:15:20.557
I also entertain little children.

00:15:20.581 --> 00:15:25.363
And when you get an entire
huge audience of children --

00:15:25.387 --> 00:15:31.117
dead silence, listening and waiting
and giving you all their attention --